    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/b5fef7bcf8f4b842741ebc12aeb0ae14.avif?t=1700917745\" width=618 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>Ahoy sailors!</strong> Welcome to <strong>ARGH!</strong>, a 3D Battle Royale where you will have to come up with the best strategies to survive.<br><br>Navigate your boat skillfully and be ready to explore every nook and cranny of the map!<br>As you explore, collect and use wisely the various treasures of the seas to get rid of the opposing captains and build a solid reputation across the oceans!<br>However, watch out for the Oblivion! This scourge sweeps memories away and sinks unsuccessful captains into oblivion... So, raise your bounty to the highest level and build an unforgettable legend!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/d937cacea70f4d067b68f6fee640ff67.avif?t=1700917745\" width=620 height=79 /></span><br><br>- Play as one of 3 unique captains of ARGH! and compete against 6 players in a resource-filled arena.<br><br>- Explore the various islands and loot their abundant treasures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/e796be2c5633695cc7c5a733ada9ff87.poster.avif?t=1700917745\" width=596 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/e796be2c5633695cc7c5a733ada9ff87.webm?t=1700917745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/e796be2c5633695cc7c5a733ada9ff87.mp4?t=1700917745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Use these treasures to attack other ships!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/2b4078385a48c6e8ee33171de9203bc0.poster.avif?t=1700917745\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/2b4078385a48c6e8ee33171de9203bc0.webm?t=1700917745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175150/extras/2b4078385a48c6e8ee33171de9203bc0.mp4?t=1700917745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Adapt to each situation! Is fighting really the best option?<br><br>- Keep an eye on the Oblivion and its progress to avoid fading from memory.<br><br>- Achieve great feats to earn the highest bounty in the Seven Seas!",
